<knowl mode="exercise" xmlns="https://spatext.clontz.org" version="0.2">
    <intro>
        <p>
            Consider a function <m>p(x)</m> defined by <me>p(x):=\sum_{n=0}^\infty {{sn}}x^n.</me>
        </p>
    </intro>
    <knowl>
        <content><p>Find <m>p_{ {{k}} }(x)</m>, the degree <m>{{k}}</m> polynomial approximation for <m>p(x)</m>.</p></content>
        <outtro><p> <m> p_{ {{k}} }(x)={{pk}}</m>.</p></outtro>
    </knowl>
    <knowl>
        <content><p>Use <m>p_{ {{k}} }(x)</m> to estimate <m>p({{c}})</m>.</p></content>
        <outtro><p><m>p_{ {{k}} }({{c}}) = {{pkc}}</m>.</p></outtro>
    </knowl>
